data.description: his well-maintained country residence, resting on an expansive lot of nearly one acre, benefits from city water and natural gas utilities. The property features two outbuildings, each approximately 12 x 12 in size, thoughtfully designed to complement the home's style, along with a covered patio area. Inside, you'll find a cozy fireplace, convenient indoor laundry facilities, and ample space for animals. The home comprises three bedrooms, two bathrooms, totaling 1,579 square feet of living space, and a charming dining nook, all within a vintage 1970 build, just outside Stratford, California.
